### Register
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "phone": "0123456789",
  "password": "secret123",
  "email": "john@example.com"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "0123456789",
  "password": "secret123"
}

